== 制作 ==
导演麦克斯·巴巴考夫和编剧安迪·西亚拉在[[美国电影学院|美国电影学院]]读书的时候，就想出了影片的概念，“为低预算影片写剧本时将[[荣格|荣格]]的心理学概念及[[语用学|语用学]]重要性融为一体，出来的影片会很容易制作”<ref name="avclub">{{cite web |last=Siede |first=Caroline |title=Palm Springs is the definitive 2020 rom-com |url=https://film.avclub.com/palm-springs-is-the-definitive-2020-rom-com-1845771883 |website=A.V. Club |accessdate=2021-02-17 |date=2020-04-12 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210041837/https://film.avclub.com/palm-springs-is-the-definitive-2020-rom-com-1845771883 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他们在编剧时参考了荒诞喜剧[[呢喃核|呢喃核]]电影《[[离开拉斯维加斯|离开拉斯维加斯]]》，这部电影讲述一位30岁出头的落魄男子想到棕榈泉自杀，结果渐渐发现他活着的意义<ref name="avclub"/>。西亚拉继续给电视剧《{{le|49号旅舍|Lodge 49}}》编剧的时候，两人从科幻片角度重新开发剧本，务求打造更具野心的作品<ref>{{cite web |date= 2020-07-07 |last= Erbland |first= Kate |author-link=  |title= How 'Palm Springs' Transformed from 'Leaving Las Vegas' Rip-Off to a Sci-Fi 'Groundhog Day' |url= https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/palm-springs-andy-siara-interview/ |website= IndieWire |accessdate= 2021-02-17 |archive-date= 2021-02-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210217141933/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/palm-springs-andy-siara-interview-1234571046/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。《[[今天暫時停止|今天暫時停止]]》是率先使用时间循环元素的浪漫喜剧，巴巴考夫和西亚拉编剧的时候，想尽量脱离这部影片的影子。这使得主角奈尔斯在开头就已经在时间循环中，让影片看起来像是“一部不存在电影的续集”，之后第二个角色莎拉加入循环，起到指引观众的作用<ref name="TheRingerPalmSprings">{{cite web | url = https://www.theringer.com/movies/2020/7/9/21317708/palm-springs-movie-making-of-andy-samberg-groundhog-day | title = How the 'Palm Springs' Team Found a New Wrinkle in the Time-Loop Movie | first = Jake | last = Kring-Schreifels | date = 2020-07-09 | access-date = 2020-07-12 | work = The Ringer | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116220651/https://www.theringer.com/movies/2020/7/9/21317708/palm-springs-movie-making-of-andy-samberg-groundhog-day | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2018年11月，计划正式公布，且获加州政府豁免收税。受此影响，剧组必须在洛杉矶取景，而不是去棕-{}-榈泉。[[安迪·萨姆伯格|安迪·萨姆伯格]]将担任主演<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.desertsun.com/story/news/2018/11/19/andy-sambergs-palm-springs-film-could-get-millions-tax-credits/2031461002/|title=SNL alum Andy Samberg's 'Palm Springs' film on pace to earn $2.5 million in tax credits|website=The Desert Sun|access-date=2019-03-25|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010104423/https://www.desertsun.com/story/news/2018/11/19/andy-sambergs-palm-springs-film-could-get-millions-tax-credits/2031461002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年3月，[[克莉絲汀·米利歐提|克莉絲汀·米利歐提]]和[[J·K·西蒙斯|J·K·西蒙斯]]加盟剧组<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/palm-springs-andy-samberg-cristin-milioti-j-k-simmons-star-limelight-max-barbakow-1202573806/|title=Upstart Limelight Sets 'Palm Springs' As First Go Picture; Andy Samberg, Cristin Milioti, J.K. Simmons To Star|last=Fleming Jr.|first=Mike|date=2019-03-11|website=Deadline Hollywood|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108023534/https://deadline.com/2019/03/palm-springs-andy-samberg-cristin-milioti-j-k-simmons-star-limelight-max-barbakow-1202573806/|archive-date=2020-11-08|access-date=2019-03-25}}</ref>。4月，[[卡蜜拉·曼德絲|卡蜜拉·曼德絲]]加入<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/04/riverdale-camila-mendes-netflix-windfall-movie-palm-springs-1202591378/ |title='Riverdale's Camila Mendes To Star In Netflix Film 'Windfall'; Joins J.K. Simmons & Andy Samberg in 'Palm Springs' |accessdate=2021-02-17 |archive-date=2019-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410131358/https://deadline.com/2019/04/riverdale-camila-mendes-netflix-windfall-movie-palm-springs-1202591378/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

影片于2019年4月开拍，历时21日<ref>{{cite web |last= Bennett |first= Alanna |title= Camila Mendes Is Taking It All in Stride |url= https://www.teenvogue.com/story/camila-mendes-may-cover |website= Teen Vogue |accessdate= 2021-02-17 |archive-date= 2020-11-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201108001935/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/camila-mendes-may-cover |dead-url= no }}</ref>。{{le|卡巴松恐龙园|Cabazon Dinosaurs}}在片中出现。

== 发行 ==
影片于2020年1月26日在[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]全球首映。不久后，{{le|Neon (发行商)|Neon (distributor)|Neon}}和[[Hulu|Hulu]]买下影片发行权<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/palm-springs-near-15-million-deal-with-neon-hulu-1202842689/|title='Palm Springs' Near $15 Million Deal With Neon & Hulu – Sundance|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|date=2020-01-27|access-date=2020-01-27|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205103550/https://deadline.com/2020/01/palm-springs-near-15-million-deal-with-neon-hulu-1202842689/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据指，Neon和Hulu开出的价码高达1750万零69美元，比圣丹斯电影节史上发行价最高的电影高出0.69美元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://apnews.com/0517642df1f39105cf67958478252b7a|title='Palm Springs' sets a Sundance record in $17.5M sale|last=Coyle|first=Jake|date=2020-01-08|website=Associated Press News|accessdate=2021-02-17|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106235124/https://apnews.com/0517642df1f39105cf67958478252b7a|dead-url=no}}</ref>。将保证金计算在内，协议价格接近2200万美元<ref name="Budget">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/hulu-neon-paid-22-million-palm-springs-streamers-dominated-sundance-film-festival-1202850004/|title=Value Of Hulu/NEON 'Palm Springs' Deal Is Actually $22 Million; How Streamers Ruled 2020 Sundance|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr.|date=2020-02-03|access-date=2020-05-28|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212204857/https://deadline.com/2020/02/hulu-neon-paid-22-million-palm-springs-streamers-dominated-sundance-film-festival-1202850004/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年7月10日，影片循Hulu平台和指定汽车戏院在美国发行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.variety.com/2020/film/news/andy-samberg-palm-springs-release-date-hulu-1234618955/|title=Andy Samberg's Rom-Com 'Palm Springs' Will Debut on Hulu in July|website=Variety|first=Rebecca|last=Rubin|date=2020-05-28|access-date=2020-05-28|archive-date=2020-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528214835/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/andy-samberg-palm-springs-release-date-hulu-1234618955/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Hulu表示影片打破了平台影片上线前三天观看总人数的纪录<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/palm-springs-streaming-record-hulu-opening-weekend-1234573145/ |title= 'Palm Springs' Sets Hulu Streaming Record with Biggest Opening Weekend — Exclusive |website= IndieWire |first= Zack |last= Scharf |date= 2020-07-14 |access-date= 2020-07-14 |archive-date= 2021-01-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210126150820/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/palm-springs-streaming-record-hulu-opening-weekend-1234573145/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2020年8月，据报Hulu订阅用户中有8.1%在影片上线首月观看该片<ref>{{Cite web |title= 'Hamilton' Far Bigger Than Anything on Netflix in July, Audience Data Reveals |url= https://variety.com/vip/disney-hamilton-audience-nearly-3x-bigger-than-any-netflix-program-in-july-1234729439/ |last= Tran |first= Kevin |website= Variety |date= 2020-08-10 |access-date= 2020-08-14 |archive-date= 2020-12-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201225215308/https://variety.com/vip/disney-hamilton-audience-nearly-3x-bigger-than-any-netflix-program-in-july-1234729439/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。11月，《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》指影片位列年度流媒体直接发行作品点播榜第26位<ref>{{cite web |last= Bridge |first= Gavin |date= 2020-11-04 |url= https://variety.com/vip/data-borat-2-second-only-to-hamilton-in-most-watched-u-s-svod-movies-of-2020-1234823177/ |title= DATA: ‘BORAT 2’ SECOND ONLY TO ‘HAMILTON’ IN MOST-WATCHED U.S. SVOD MOVIES OF 2020 |website= Variety |access-date= 2020-11-04 |archive-date= 2020-11-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201104174256/https://variety.com/vip/data-borat-2-second-only-to-hamilton-in-most-watched-u-s-svod-movies-of-2020-1234823177/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2021年1月，影片{{le|音频解说|audio commentary|解说版}}上线，主创萨姆伯格、米利欧缇、巴巴考夫和西亚拉解说，是Hulu首部带解说的作品<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/palm-springs-commentary-cut-hulu-andy-samberg-1234890448/ |title=Hulu Debuts 'Palm Springs' Commentary Cut With Andy Samberg and Cristin Milioti (Exclusive) |last=Donnelly |first=Matt |date=2021-01-25 |website=Variety |access-date=2021-02-01 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204020512/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/palm-springs-commentary-cut-hulu-andy-samberg-1234890448/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
=== 票房 ===
影片上映首周末登陆66家影院，总票房16.4万美元<ref name="DeadlineGross">{{Cite web |url= https://deadline.com/2020/07/star-wars-empire-strikes-back-tops-weekend-box-office-drive-ins-coronavirus-1202983364/ |title= 'Empire Strikes Back' Leads At The Weekend Box Office With $644K, 23 Years After Sequel's Special Edition – Update |author= Anthony D'Alessandro |website= Deadline Hollywood |date= 2020-07-13 |access-date= 2020-07-13 |archive-date= 2020-12-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201212064125/https://deadline.com/2020/07/star-wars-empire-strikes-back-tops-weekend-box-office-drive-ins-coronavirus-1202983364/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>，次周末在约30家影院上映，票房10.1万美元<ref name=IndieWireGrosses>{{Cite web |title= 'The Outpost' Still Strong on VOD, While John Lewis and Danny Trejo Docs Score |url= https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/vod-charts-outpost-john-lewis-danny-trejo-documentaries-1234575163/ |last= Brueggemann |first= Tom |website= IndieWire |date= 2020-07-21 |access-date= 2020-07-21 |archive-date= 2020-11-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201123113608/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/vod-charts-outpost-john-lewis-danny-trejo-documentaries-1234575163/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
汇总媒体[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]评论212条，新鲜度94%，平均得分8/10。网站共识写道：“出色的表演、扎实的导演方向、耳目一新的原创概念将《棕榈泉》打造成一部让人很容易爱上的浪漫喜剧<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/palm_springs_2020 |title= Palm Springs (2020) |website= Rotten Tomatoes |access-date= 2021-01-11 |archive-date= 2020-11-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201105224704/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/palm_springs_2020 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]评论42条，加权平均分83/100，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web |url= https://metacritic.com/movie/palm-springs |title= Palm Springs Reviews |website= Metacritic |access-date= 2020-09-05 |archive-date= 2021-02-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210217141953/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/palm-springs |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

《[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]》专栏作家大卫·埃里希（David Ehrlich）给出B+的评级，认可电影巧妙复刻了《[[今天暫時停止|今天暫時停止]]》的公式：“影片由头到尾都想做活力十足的90分钟喜剧片不一定能做的事情，仿佛有点不自量力，而剧情上的逼人气势也丝毫不给剧情节奏放缓的机会<ref>{{cite web |date= 2020-01-27 |last= Ehrlich |first= David |title= 'Palm Springs' Review: Andy Samberg and The Lonely Island Brilliantly Reinvent the 'Groundhog Day' Formula |url= https://www.indiewire.com/2020/01/palm-springs-review-andy-samberg-sundance-1202206545/ |website= IndieWire |access-date= 2020-06-17 |archive-date= 2020-11-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201123113802/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/01/palm-springs-review-andy-samberg-sundance-1202206545/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的彼得·德布鲁格（Peter Debruge）给出正面评价，认为“《棕榈泉》之于时间循环片，如同《[[屍樂園|屍樂園]]》之于僵尸片。《棕榈泉》在形式上深入撼动了前辈的影片，让它们开始审慎考虑自己的地位”<ref>{{cite web |date= 2020-01-28 |last= Debruge |first= Peter |title= 'Palm Springs': Film Review |url= https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/palm-springs-review-1203482914/ |website= Variety |access-date= 2020-06-17 |archive-date= 2020-11-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201123114027/https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/palm-springs-review-1203482914/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。《{{le|Uproxx|Uproxx}}》给出正面评价，认为影片是完美的艺术喜剧片，“出场的时候像很聪明天真的小百灵鸟，最终一堆砖块变成砸到你身上<ref>{{cite web |url= https://uproxx.com/movies/palm-springs-review-andy-samberg-hulu/ |title= 'Palm Springs' Is Silly, Stylish, Profound, And Damn Near Perfect |author= Vince Mancini |website= Uproxx |date= 2020-07-07 |access-date= 2020-07-12 |archive-date= 2021-01-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210114122110/https://uproxx.com/movies/palm-springs-review-andy-samberg-hulu/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

影片入选Metacritic2020年度甄选片单第12位<ref>{{cite web |title=Best of 2020: Film Critic Top Ten Lists |url=https://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-pick-10-best-movies-of-2020 |website=Metacritic |access-date=2020-12-26 |archive-date=2020-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215081138/https://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-pick-10-best-movies-of-2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，入选[[IGN|IGN]]2020年度最佳电影<ref>{{cite web |title=Best Movie of the Year 2020 |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/best-movies-of-2020 |website=ign.com |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114142204/https://www.ign.com/articles/best-movies-of-2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

